<HEADLINE> Eminem Daughter Will Live With Wife  </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
   MOUNT CLEMENS, Mich. (AP) -- Rap star Eminem has agreed to give
up physical custody of his 5-year-old daughter to his estranged
wife.
</P>
<P>
   Eminem on Monday also agreed to continue financial support of
wife Kim Mathers, provide a driver for her and reinstate her credit
cards.
</P>
<P>
   In exchange, Eminem, whose real name is Marshall Mathers, will
have joint legal custody of the couple's daughter and be entitled
to liberal parenting time while in Michigan.
</P>
